      "text": "We’re coming to understand the power of capturing and sharing stories of learning within our community. Our school story and our personal stories, both have immense power. Sharing allows us to become seen and heard and to feel alive. Story telling is a gift to others but also a gift to ourselves. In sharing, we bravely step into and own  our truth. Illuminating our stories imparts a feeling that can't be 'un-felt' by others. They sense life in the journey and the learning. Learning feels as if it is alive. "
